the middle of finding its purpose [ https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFUM=
uOhCAQ_JrhaAAB8cBhL_MbhkePQwbBIO6uf7-tHjYhdEF1U1R522Au9TBr2Ro5t6kdK5gMP1uC1=
